        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "3）上千条仍卡就换虚拟列表；滚动计算用 "
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "requestAnimationFrame"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": " 或节流，避免一帧算多次。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "strong",
            "value": "示例："
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "底部哨兵 + IntersectionObserver。"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "code",
            "value": "const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n  if (entries[0].isIntersecting) loadMore()\n})\nio.observe(sentryEl)"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
